        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0020017"/>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">TODO: move to skos:definition

A birth name is a family name that a woman had before marriage.</rdfs:comment>
